{"tid":2209134,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)新特警判官 猛火爆1-2 重案夢幻組2","createTime":"2020-09-19T12:07:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T20:04:14.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"58a3f76c5629d82726fda40fb7f8c52074c2e180","tid":2209134,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T12:07:21.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">新沙士已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=1nW%2FAbATR%2BcU2iH%2BEMdxE3ljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=7aa7ba2e\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=1nW%2FAbATR%2BcU2iH%2BEMdxE3ljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=ec98f7b7\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=1nW%2FAbATR%2BcU2iH%2BEMdxE3ljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=81a3ec2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/1/16/Dredd2012Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F1%2F16%2FDredd2012Poster.jpg&h=966cac5f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/9e/RED_2_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F9e%2FRED_2_poster.jpg&h=3c316e90&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/d/d0/Bad_boys_two.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fd%2Fd0%2FBad_boys_two.jpg&h=d5347368&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.未來，美國變成了一片人稱詛咒之地的反烏托邦荒原，受到核輻射的嚴重污染。位於東海岸的超級城市一號中生活有8億居民，是一個暴力叢生的超級大都市，平均每天都會報告1.7萬起犯罪事件。這裡新出現了一種名為「慢動作」的毒品，可以讓人感知到的時間減慢到正常水平的1%。城中唯一用於維持秩序的公權力叫「判官」，擁有法官、陪審團和行刑人三種權力於一身<br />\n<br />\n2.法蘭克莫西斯（Frank Moses；布魯斯&middot;威利飾演）是一名自CIA退休的前特工，被CIA的分類為RED，即為已退休而極度危險的（Retired, Extremely Dangerous），他感到退休生活十分無趣沒有變化，唯一的樂趣是每月撕毀養老金支票藉故與養老金管理人莎拉羅斯（Sarah Ross；瑪莉&middot;露易絲&middot;派克飾演）在電話裡的談天說地時間，且法蘭克對莎拉在心中漸生情愫；一日法蘭克家中突然闖入了數名傭兵，想要將法蘭克滅口，法蘭克憑著過去的矯健身手將傭兵團擊退後，發現攻擊的背後有著巨大的陰謀存在；因此為了保護所愛的人，法蘭克決定召集過去的老戰友們，來對抗陰謀的幕後黑手並揭發真相&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n3.出生入死、爾虞我詐的諜報世界裡，你要相信薑是老的辣！退而不休，寶刀未老的探員法蘭克（布魯斯威利 飾）憑著往昔經驗和過人能耐，將與他的昔日戰友再度出手，不但要拯救世界免於核子威脅，更要保全他們自己的老命...<br />\n<br />\n4.在第一部電影之後8年，警探麥克&middot;勞里（Mike Lowrey，威爾&middot;史密斯飾演）和馬奎斯&middot;巴涅特（Marcus Burnett，馬丁&middot;勞倫斯飾演）正在追查進入邁阿密的迷幻藥源頭。他們追蹤著幾隻來自古巴，來到一個三K黨聚會，毒品也在這裡進行交易。在交火中，麥克意外射傷了馬奎斯的臀部，使得馬奎斯開始考慮自己是否想要和麥克繼續搭檔<br />\n<br />\n8 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=1nW%2FAbATR%2BcU2iH%2BEMdxE3ljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=9f76f722\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=1nW%2FAbATR%2BcU2iH%2BEMdxE3ljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=294f8d9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"313ce5560f63e6e5565d1eb2bf7a14d757231e3f","tid":2209134,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T12:08:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ed2e5cf846393c5e14489ab1e8956d3d44ecd84","tid":2209134,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T12:56:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82d94384694c679339868e209d56fcea5f83e8e1","tid":2209134,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T14:17:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c31275335bc4dc56c9d3718bebc8dcb094b219f","tid":2209134,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T15:56:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c054349540bb4ef6d1c358120ff1d8c3ea16046","tid":2209134,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T16:44:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56c0ac067699aa515b5276549f1512b84c0ceb34","tid":2209134,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T18:50:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=